channel.description:
[center][b]What is EvasionRSPS?[/b][/center]
[center]Evasion is simply a server where you kill a penguin pick up it's crystal key and open a chest and get a reward. You may ask.. That's it? No it is not, we have 6 locations in total primal,pengs,phats,monkey and farmers which all of them drop items from buckets to nex items. We are currently looking for staff[/center]
[center]http://www.rswebclients.com/client/evasionv2[/center]
